  • Classes in BestSoFar.framework.core used by BestSoFar.framework.core 
    Class and Description
    AbstractElement
    Abstract implementation of Element for elemental processors to extend, which requires a one-to-one mapping of input data to output data (without training necessary).
    AbstractWorkflow
    Abstract implementation of Workflow.
    AbstractWorkflowContainer
    Abstract implementation of WorkflowContainer.
    Element
    An Element is a Processor which sits inside a Workflow.
    Processor
    The top-level interface for all parts of the workflow framework.
    Workflow
    A workflow is a linear list of Element objects which sits in a WorkflowContainer.
    WorkflowContainer
    A WorkflowContainer is an Element that contains one or more Workflow objects.
    WorkflowImpl
    Implementation of Workflow.
